data.description: Calling all INVESTORS! GREAT LOCATION!! Occupied through March 2024.. Let somebody else pay majority of your mortgage!  Why Not?  This is a GREAT area, close to dining, shopping, and great parks!!    Professionally managed by RPM of The Triad. This property Offers 2 Bedrooms & 2 Full Baths, Family Room, Spacious Kitchen With an abundance of counter space AND cabinet space!  Home Wty conveys with acceptable Offer.  ** eat in area currently being used for storage**   1 assigned parking space and plenty of open parking for guests!  Water is included with HOA!!  Don't let this opportunity get away from YOU!
